&gt; Alright. I surrender. All the comments and sarcasm make it clear to me
&gt; that my points and attempts here are lost. I&#39;m not new to the field
&gt; and I know the importance of having some protocol but... not everyone
&gt; feels the same. That&#39;s okay. Unless your like Frank R and are only in
&gt; this for yourself, then your truly not a serious researcher in the
&gt; true definition of the word.
&gt;
Is it just me who is not a serious researcher or do you mean us all?  
(Excepting Frank R., who is... misguided? Selfish?)

Am I misunderstanding you this time? You seem very misunderstood in  
general, don&#39;t you think?

That&#39;s the end of this, babs. I&#39;ve two hours of box research to  
either not hear correctly, tweak into something its not, not really  
get because I&#39;m not 1 of 30, or not follow your protocols in cataloging.

Ann
Falsely serious researcher extraordinaire.


